      <title>菲律宾称与中国的海上紧张局势并未损害经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/philippines-says-sea-tensions-with-china-have-not-hurt-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾表示，与北京的地缘政治紧张局势并未影响这个东南亚国家的经济，政府仍愿意与中国投资者合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/philippines-says-sea-tensions-with-china-have-not-hurt-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 04:22:53 GMT</pubDate>
