      <title>卡梅伦瞄准其他欧洲国家的国防开支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/cameron-takes-aim-at-other-european-nations-on-defense-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦将批评其他欧洲国家“不愿意”投资国防，同时他敦促西方民主国家在保护其利益和价值观方面“更加强硬、更加自信”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/cameron-takes-aim-at-other-european-nations-on-defense-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
